{"tid":756152,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"其實係咪粵語歌詞先要岩哂個音? 咁難作?","createTime":"2018-07-25T21:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T15:03:28.000Z","uid":294,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b683b659b8cf186bc81303aaffbd800bd4a34274","tid":756152,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T21:27:50.000Z","msg":"國語 同一個字放落任何音度都岩, eg我字: 禾, 鍋, 禍<br />\n<br />\n日本, 英文都係咁<br />\n<br />\n但粵語一唔中正果個音就變教會歌<br />\n<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f703d3d066cc4d504874da71ab27092d94cab8d7","tid":756152,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T21:33:03.000Z","msg":"同埋隻字啲音調可唔可以特登高/低<br />\n利申：五音不全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e923caef0666292f72289723167291553edc1aea","tid":756152,"uid":11598,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T21:44:45.000Z","msg":"好多因素 簡單啲講就係聲調多好多 mandarin有4 聲，廣東話有 9 聲 <br />\n自然啲字重音率低咗，同一個音就會得好少啱用嘅字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fda571eae8ef2b090fa2ab867803f5ebd47b11a","tid":756152,"uid":31215,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T21:55:08.000Z","msg":"廣東歌難作過國語英文歌<br />\n但普遍廣東歌詞有深度過國語英文歌"},{"pid":"0f78faa0c5737e8f4e3164121e3335f70c8761d6","tid":756152,"uid":61840,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2fda571eae8ef2b090fa2ab867803f5ebd47b11a","tid":756152,"uid":31215,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T21:55:08.000Z","msg":"廣東歌難作過國語英文歌<br />\n但普遍廣東歌詞有深度過國語英文歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T22:14:12.000Z","msg":"普遍叫春多"},{"pid":"feb7abd12e63fedc81de5fd0f0f9b4efc5c5514b","tid":756152,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fda571eae8ef2b090fa2ab867803f5ebd47b11a","tid":756152,"uid":31215,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-